                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                公司為現今社會經濟生活中最基本及重要的企業組織，亦為現代經濟活動的主體，而公司法為其規範之根本法，欲瞭解現代企業組織運作者，不可不修習公司法。又鑑於中國大陸於世界中經濟地位之重要性，已不容忽視，再加上兩岸間經貿關係的密切性，深入研究並瞭解大陸法制已成為一項必要的課題。本課程將擇傳統商事法中之公司法制中的重要議題作為本專題研究課程之內容，並比較分析大陸與台灣公司法制之異同。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                This course of Seminar on Laws and Regulations between Taiwan strait will focus upon the laws and regulations governing corporation. An analysis of the fundamental structure and concepts of present Company Law will be given and further to explore the difference between Taiwan and China Company Law in hope that the students can have a full understanding of its theory and application in practice. We will first introduce the general meanings and features of corporate law; then to elaborate the contents and provisions of company law on the basis of the methodology of comparative law.











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





